  "title": "AB03 - Delivery Driver (Class 3 & 3A License)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Class 3/3A Driver (Parcel Delivery)</strong><br />Salary: Basic $2000 + OT<br />Working days & hours: 5.5 days (Mon-Fri) 8am-6pm, (Sat/Sun) 9.30am till deliver finished goods (1 or 2pm end)<br />Working Location: Report to Greenwich Dr (Near Buangkok / Hougang)<br /><br /><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible of delivering goods to customers.</li><li>Loading/unloading goods.</li><li>Warehouse management.</li><li>Maintain the cleanliness of vehicles.</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Possess class 3 or 3A driving license</li><li>On job training provided</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
